Here, I'll get a spoon for you.

00:18:06.117 --> 00:18:07.200
MICHAEL BRENNER: Here we--

00:18:07.200 --> 00:18:08.940
MICHAEL VOLTAGGIO: While they're
doing the unimportant stuff--

00:18:08.940 --> 00:18:09.290
BRYAN VOLTAGGIO: Here--

00:18:09.290 --> 00:18:10.480
MICHAEL VOLTAGGIO: --I'm
going to finish my dish.

00:18:10.480 --> 00:18:11.360
BRYAN VOLTAGGIO: I'll come around.

00:18:11.360 --> 00:18:13.330
MICHAEL VOLTAGGIO: So
we're still on the air.

00:18:13.330 --> 00:18:14.540
We're not paying attention to them.

00:18:14.540 --> 00:18:14.780
BRYAN VOLTAGGIO: You got it?

00:18:14.780 --> 00:18:15.440
OK.

00:18:15.440 --> 00:18:16.910
MICHAEL BRENNER: This is so great.

00:18:16.910 --> 00:18:20.320
MICHAEL VOLTAGGIO: Is that even
calibrated, that microscope over there?

00:18:20.320 --> 00:18:21.604
