00:18:21.604 --> 00:18:22.770
MICHAEL BRENNER: Absolutely.

00:18:22.770 --> 00:18:23.720
MICHAEL VOLTAGGIO: OK.

00:18:23.720 --> 00:18:28.810
So now the foam is in
the nitrogen. There's

00:18:28.810 --> 00:18:31.580
gas trapped inside of
that liquid or solid.

00:18:31.580 --> 00:18:33.665
And so now I can just break that up.

00:18:33.665 --> 00:18:36.090
