my house or in a restaurant.

00:46:52.260 --> 00:46:55.600
So what we do is we take-- the
pasta always goes into the pan.

00:46:55.600 --> 00:46:56.620
It gets tossed together.

00:46:56.620 --> 00:46:59.161
The agitation is one thing that
helps to create the emulsion.

00:46:59.161 --> 00:47:01.750
But then it's also the starch
that's coming also off the pasta

00:47:01.750 --> 00:47:07.350
